    "guide.title": "Getting Started with Keto: The First Two Weeks",
    "guide.subtitle": "A step-by-step guide to navigating the induction phase, managing side effects, and setting yourself up for long-term success.",
    "guide.intro": "The first two weeks of a ketogenic diet are where the biggest metabolic changes happen. Your body is moving from sugar-burning to fat- and ketone-burning, your hormones are adjusting, and your brain is learning to run on a new fuel. This guide walks you through:",
    "guide.intro.list1": "How to prepare medically and safely",
