    "guide.step1.title": "1. Medical Preparation",
    "guide.step1.intro": "Before embarking on a ketogenic diet, it's best to treat it like any other serious therapeutic intervention, not just a casual \"diet.\"",
    "guide.step1.history": "Review Your Health History",
    "guide.step1.history.desc": "Sit down with your healthcare provider and review:",
    "guide.step1.history.list1": "History of kidney disease, liver disease, pancreatitis, gallstones",
    "guide.step1.history.list2": "Any diagnosis of diabetes (type 1 or type 2) or prediabetes",
